{"tid":2331110,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"KBS歌謠大祝祭2020︱TWICE等戴口罩行紅地氈　子瑜Mina性感搶鏡","createTime":"2020-12-18T13:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T14:56:27.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"14d15db43e8d71048e5a329aed3ea20edc84826b","tid":2331110,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"一年一度的「KBS歌謠大祝祭」今天（18日）舉行，雖然韓國新冠肺炎疫情嚴重，但一樣無阻節目如期舉行。BTS防彈少年團、TWICE、GOT7、MAMAMOO、IZ*ONE和ITZY等多組人氣偶像更率先現身紅地氈，可是眾人都要戴口罩上陣，略為可惜。<br />\n<br />\n今天紅地氈意外地由BTS防彈少年團打頭陣出場，Suga仍在休養當中。由於已一段時間未能與粉絲見面，六人用韓英兩語對世界各地粉絲打招呼，V更特別走到鏡頭前向粉絲派福利。其後SHINee泰民、NU&rsquo;EST、TXT都有陸續土場，其中以22人上陣的NCT最為有氣勢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201218/416688639297196032684120.jpeg/Rznm4TtjGKyu1bPbh9RFLpTpFgpiDeXm-HMwpPhzMKQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201218%2F416688639297196032684120.jpeg%2FRznm4TtjGKyu1bPbh9RFLpTpFgpiDeXm-HMwpPhzMKQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e7827e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女團方面，上月才出道的SM娛樂新人女團aespa終於首次現身公開場合，其中最多是非的&lrm;Karina身穿低胸長裙上陣，大曬隱藏級好身材，意外吸睛！而IZ*ONE、ITZY和MAMAOO大部份都以短裙短褲現身，幸好今年紅地氈在室內舉行，一眾女偶像都不如捱凍上陣。TWICE則繼續只有7位成員現身，Sana雖然已完成自我隔離，但為安全起見，今晚缺席KBS歌謠大祝祭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201218/416688938384625664689231.jpeg/EOGU0fAiJgDZnzPIgGe5oZhY26xkRZ35Ncbc7TXG3O0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201218%2F416688938384625664689231.jpeg%2FEOGU0fAiJgDZnzPIgGe5oZhY26xkRZ35Ncbc7TXG3O0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=743f4095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201218/416689545229111296365142.jpeg/NhHLgcISfvtKhAuD_a4tgncYNDPC8gHXBuOQAwbjkAM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201218%2F416689545229111296365142.jpeg%2FNhHLgcISfvtKhAuD_a4tgncYNDPC8gHXBuOQAwbjkAM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=451f53c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},